23:["$","p","38",{"className":"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4","children":"**Price:** $199 | **Rating:** 4.4/5 | **Capacity:** 3 lbs"}]
24:["$","p","39",{"className":"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4","children":"The PETLIBRO Air offers smart WiFi control at a mid-range price point, ideal for cats needing flexible scheduling."}]
25:["$","p","40",{"className":"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4","children":"**Key Features:**\n- WiFi app control from anywhere\n- Supports up to 6 meals per day for grazing behavior\n- Portion scheduling down to 1/8 cup increments\n- Sealed food chamber prevents odor and oxidation\n- Compact design (smallest smart feeder on market)"}]
